<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title><%= title %></title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, sans-serif;
            max-width: 700px;
            margin: 50px auto;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
        }
        .success-container {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #d4edda 0%, #c3e6cb 100%);
            border: 2px solid #28a745;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 30px;
            text-align: center;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        .success-icon {
            font-size: 48px;
            color: #28a745;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .attempt-summary {
            background: white;
            border-radius: 6px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            text-align: left;
        }
        .progress-bar {
            width: 100%;
            height: 20px;
            background: #e9ecef;
            border-radius: 10px;
            overflow: hidden;
            margin: 15px 0;
        }
        .progress-fill {
            height: 100%;
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, #28a745, #20c997);
            width: 100%;
            transition: width 0.3s ease;
        }
        .retry-stats {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(150px, 1fr));
            gap: 15px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .stat-box {
            background: white;
            border: 1px solid #28a745;
            border-radius: 6px;
            padding: 15px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .stat-number {
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #28a745;
        }
        .stat-label {
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #6c757d;
            text-transform: uppercase;
        }
        .status-badge {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 4px 12px;
            border-radius: 12px;
            font-size: 14px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: white;
            background: #28a745;
        }
        .celebration {
            font-size: 24px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="success-container">
        <div class="success-icon">ðŸŽ‰</div>
        <h1><%= title %></h1>
        <div class="celebration">ðŸŽŠ Retry Logic Successful! ðŸŽŠ</div>
        <p><%= message %></p>
        
        <div class="attempt-summary">
            <h3>Retry Summary</h3>
            <div style="display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; margin-bottom: 10px;">
                <span><strong>Final Attempt:</strong> <%= attempt %></span>
                <span class="status-badge">SUCCESS</span>
            </div>
            
            <div class="progress-bar">
                <div class="progress-fill"></div>
            </div>
            
            <p style="margin: 10px 0 0 0;">
                âœ… <strong>Request succeeded after <%= failedAttempts %> failed attempts</strong>
            </p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="retry-stats">
            <div class="stat-box">
                <div class="stat-number"><%= failedAttempts %></div>
                <div class="stat-label">Failed Attempts</div>
            </div>
            <div class="stat-box">
                <div class="stat-number">1</div>
                <div class="stat-label">Successful Attempt</div>
            </div>
            <div class="stat-box">
                <div class="stat-number"><%= attempt %></div>
                <div class="stat-label">Total Attempts</div>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <div style="background: #d4edda; border: 1px solid #c3e6cb; border-radius: 4px; padding: 15px; margin: 20px 0;">
            <h4>âœ… Retry Test Results</h4>
            <ul style="text-align: left;">
                <li><strong>Resilience:</strong> Your client successfully handled <%= failedAttempts %> consecutive failures</li>
                <li><strong>Persistence:</strong> Retry logic continued until success was achieved</li>
                <li><strong>Recovery:</strong> System recovered gracefully from temporary failures</li>
                <li><strong>Reliability:</strong> Final request completed successfully</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
        
        <div style="background: #e7f3ff; border: 1px solid #b3d9ff; border-radius: 4px; padding: 15px; margin: 20px 0;">
            <h4>ðŸ§ª Testing Validation</h4>
            <p><strong>This success confirms:</strong></p>
            <ul style="text-align: left;">
                <li>Retry mechanism is working correctly</li>
                <li>Error handling doesn't give up too early</li>
                <li>Exponential backoff (if implemented) allowed recovery</li>
                <li>Final success was properly detected and processed</li>
            </ul>
            
            <p><strong>Next steps:</strong></p>
            <ul style="text-align: left;">
                <li>Test with different failure counts using <code>?fail=N</code></li>
                <li>Verify retry delays are appropriate</li>
                <li>Test batch processing with mixed success/failure</li>
                <li>Reset counters with <code>POST /error/flaky/reset</code></li>
            </ul>
        </div>
        
        <div style="background: #f8f9fa; border-radius: 4px; padding: 15px; margin: 20px 0;">
            <h4>Content for PDF Generation</h4>
            <p>This successful page can now be converted to PDF, demonstrating that the retry logic allowed the conversion to complete despite initial failures.</p>
            
            <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: 10px; margin: 15px 0;">
                <div style="background: #28a745; color: white; padding: 10px; border-radius: 4px; text-align: center;">
                    <strong>Resilient</strong>
                </div>
                <div style="background: #17a2b8; color: white; padding: 10px; border-radius: 4px; text-align: center;">
                    <strong>Reliable</strong>
                </div>
                <div style="background: #ffc107; color: #212529; padding: 10px; border-radius: 4px; text-align: center;">
                    <strong>Robust</strong>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>